Package: MIMIC4db
Title: Package for building, loading and referencing the Google BigQuery verion of the MIMIC-IV
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "H. David",
           family = "Shea",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "hdshea@comcast.net")
Description: This package provides a tightly bound set of routines access the Google BigQuery version 
    of the MIMIC-IV database.  These access routines include metadata definitions, base data access functions,
    and higher level data access functions that encapsulate common patterns for data access for research
    data analytic processes.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
